Package src

Class ComponentsList

java.lang.Object
src.ComponentsList
public class ComponentsList extends Object
Stores a collection of motherboards, CPUs, GPUs, RAM configurations, PSUs, storage options, and screen panels. Provide easy access to each category through HashMaps and key lists, where the key lists are selected and the corresponding HashMap key receives the input and gets imported to a component object.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Ahmed-Hassan Odtallah
